{"tid":379020,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"畫左火影十五年 你問我答","createTime":"2017-08-29T02:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T22:48:20.000Z","uid":105237,"like":3,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42d01d52f3b7d85b0cecb9e7994600fb3036a454","tid":379020,"uid":105237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T02:41:37.000Z","msg":"首先要多謝各位連登會員近日一直出火影既討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見大家都好熱烈討論 <br />\n<br />\n有見及此 有咩問題都可以係度問我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79e7d969bb04ad65ad58c993f37417dbcbb2fa4","tid":379020,"uid":4557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T02:42:20.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"d146f25b81d4dd334d17d74f118df9fb9c3a11f7","tid":379020,"uid":85909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T02:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出完鳴人個仔會唔會出佢個孫跟住無限loop"},{"pid":"2449b715a1205f116cbe3aa6829f9b04ce50564c","tid":379020,"uid":105237,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T02:46:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>圖呢</blockquote><br />\n見你地咁鐘意鳴佐 圖呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/29/104551_da872791b27160ff03eccaa1a96263a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F29%2F104551_da872791b27160ff03eccaa1a96263a5.jpg&h=82c6d6af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f713a7324ea86b7957f7468123ea0922e0baacd","tid":379020,"uid":105237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T02:47:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出完鳴人個仔會唔會出佢個孫跟住無限loop</blockquote><br />\n其實我已經半退休緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依層就要睇下助手生唔生性"},{"pid":"53513a094b362ebdc7b043f9c84aa8b9abf5d445","tid":379020,