e":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:10:54.000Z","msg":"自來也死真係喊左<br />\n屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d98aea7b7beff11ab8d64d7ebfbc739eee6cac","tid":379020,"uid":105237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:16:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自來也死真係喊左<br />\n屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好榮幸可以令你濕左<br />\n多謝支持<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/29/111602_a756647afd46abc22534d3a616a061d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F29%2F111602_a756647afd46abc22534d3a616a061d8.jpg&h=1a96d170&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2704123377bcbb0ecf1e4fa87379e0d257d4069","tid":379020,"uid":124951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:35:49.000Z","msg":"你做得最啱就係無穢土好色仙人"},{"pid":"ecbca65148f8563ff11c1fab7b10fe3ef13a133a","tid":379020,"uid":105237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:49:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你做得最啱就係無穢土好色仙人</blockquote><br />\n如果寫自來也穢土既話 <br />\n佢用通靈術召喚蛤蟆果陣個劇情就好難寫<br />\n所以都廢事寫佢出黎 破壞自來也係大家心目中形象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0197b71fa39c94808f870e3de64c33a9ac99f74","tid":379020,"uid":129142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:53:34.000Z","msg":"點解你會識中文嘅 google translate?"},{"pid":"1aa6911a33031f67cd5658c81d7e7e3199a55337","tid":379020,"uid":39853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:00:03.000Z","msg":"全盛鼬同木葉開創初期嘅斑打邊個贏"},{"pid":"f8c71a38602f535485e1bc64021466755e7173c3","tid":379020,"uid":105237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:15:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解你會識中文嘅 google translate?</blockquote><br />\n因為我會將腰痛既時間拎黎學中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b268ea4ef85ed141a246dce7dedfe7926018c26","tid":379020,"uid":105237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:19:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全盛鼬同木葉開創初期嘅斑打邊個贏</blockquote><br />\n班生於亂世 戰鬥經驗同觸覺都會比較優勝<br />\n始終鼬出世之後就無打過大戰<br />\n基本上鼬出晒一輪大技之後就唔夠查克拉比班狂屠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8108aecdd6303d33e8fd0d89894456f573365a","tid":379020,"uid":136119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:23:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>全盛鼬同木葉開創初期嘅斑打邊個贏</blockquote><br />\n班生於亂世 戰鬥經驗同觸覺都會比較優勝<br />\n始終鼬出世之後就無打過大戰<br />\n基本上鼬出晒一輪大技之後就唔夠查克拉比班狂屠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n十拳劍都唔夠做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"c94c413258efe64adeef7c8a9cd4d0089be8163c","tid":379020,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:33:35.000Z","msg":"初代到底教左佐助咩秘術？"},{"pid":"9f7bff363737feb92ad5fbe86b8a2c34e1c02c31","tid":379020,"uid":105237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:40:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>全盛鼬同木葉開創初期嘅斑打邊個贏</blockquote><br />\n班生於亂世 戰鬥經驗同觸覺都會比較優勝<br />\n始終鼬出世之後就無打過大戰<br />\n基本上鼬出晒一輪大技之後就唔夠查克拉比班狂屠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n十拳劍都唔夠做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n班唔會企定定比十拳劍抽插架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6abc981a9163dd2056da0a197260104ae697adfb","tid":379020,"uid":105237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:43:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>初代到底教左佐助咩秘術？</blockquote><br />\n初代話教 但可惜佐助學唔識<br />\n又唔想整衰佐助 唯有隻字不提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5edd30961fde70e37c562a1f16660d37686360","tid":379020,"uid":82404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:43:51.000Z